  "detailed_description": "<h1>加入风域大家庭！</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719130/extras/c39992f3302970c5ac2c982e6e75915a.webp?t=1749636719\" width=600 height=50 /></span>As the energy revolution led by the Moriya Shrine continues to deepen, the number of people who believe in the Moriya Shrine is gradually increasing. To counter this, the Hakurei Shrine has established the Gensokyo People's Court in the Hall of Right and Wrong, and has begun to compete for the faith of the people.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, Marisa, who had just returned from picking mushrooms, suddenly received a subpoena from the court, ordering her to attend as a defendant in a case. In front of the fair and strict judge and the seasoned and skilled prosecutor, can Marisa find the truth behind the incident and prove her innocence?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719130/extras/7c2fca35834d070dec1911d7a1193707.webp?t=1749636719\" width=600 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719130/extras/77661fd7a7dd61e7a955ee59ce0b8162.avif?t=1749636719\" width=550 height=360 /></span>After returning from picking mushrooms, she inexplicably became the defendant in the first trial of the Gensokyo People's Court. Facing the charges of the cunning prosecutor, Marisa, who was forced to become her own lawyer, can she prove her innocence?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719130/extras/deab061228c35c13fcc4a7828fc5e90c.avif?t=1749636719\" width=550 height=360 /></span>As an assistant to the Hakurei shrine miko, under the commission of Reimu Hakurei, she became the first prosecutor of Gensokyo, determined to bring all criminals to justice. Due to the very skilled tactics of Yakumo Yukari, who enjoys teasing the defendant's lawyer, the rookie lawyer Marisa has suffered a lot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719130/extras/58af3f252a42b9156513a8770fcc484a.avif?t=1749636719\" width=550 height=360 /></span>Shikieiki originally worked in the Hall of Right and Wrong, responsible for judging the deceased. After the establishment of the Gensokyo People's Court, she naturally became the judge here. As the authority in the legal field of Gensokyo, she, who is not smiling, can always punish foolish criminals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719130/extras/0428d5210ac2f86286c206ce824b4923.avif?t=1749636719\" width=550 height=360 /></span>As an expert in maintaining the public security of Gensokyo and dealing with anomalies, the shrine maiden of the Hakurei Shrine - Reimu Hakurei, has no doubt taken on the role of \"Criminal Police\". But because she can't enforce the law \"violently\" as before, she still feels a bit regretful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719130/extras/0e3df9d265dffcebb82129f168ddc25f.webp?t=1749636719\" width=600 height=50 /></span><strong>-Find evidence-</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go to the scene of the crime and find the key evidence that has been overlooked!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719130/extras/2db80a09f86e2531c3612dfc037c2d2b.poster.avif?t=1749636719\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719130/extras/2db80a09f86e2531c3612dfc037c2d2b.webm?t=1749636719\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719130/extras/2db80a09f86e2531c3612dfc037c2d2b.mp4?t=1749636719\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Participate in the trial-</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Participate in a trial, and do your best to defend the client in the courtroom!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719130/extras/b5ed1cd28e3ecea5057eee6b22f1170d.poster.avif?t=1749636719\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719130/extras/b5ed1cd28e3ecea5057eee6b22f1170d.webm?t=1749636719\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719130/extras/b5ed1cd28e3ecea5057eee6b22f1170d.mp4?t=1749636719\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Question witnesses-</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During the witness testimony stage, keep asking for details, find flaws in the testimony, and reveal the truth!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719130/extras/439c76d5c5cd1626e421e3c490b333fb.poster.avif?t=1749636719\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719130/extras/439c76d5c5cd1626e421e3c490b333fb.webm?t=1749636719\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719130/extras/439c76d5c5cd1626e421e3c490b333fb.mp4?t=1749636719\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Present evidence-</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carefully observe every piece of evidence in the case, present evidence that contradicts the opponent's speech, and shatter the opponent's logic!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719130/extras/a870fcafdd0a71e606da14d7fa06bcc7.poster.avif?t=1749636719\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719130/extras/a870fcafdd0a71e606da14d7fa06bcc7.webm?t=1749636719\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719130/extras/a870fcafdd0a71e606da14d7fa06bcc7.mp4?t=1749636719\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-Restore the truth-</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine the story fragments and restore the truth of the incident!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719130/extras/4f0a13d8f4f6ed64ed3f6c0e38af3efb.poster.avif?t=1749636719\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719130/extras/4f0a13d8f4f6ed64ed3f6c0e38af3efb.webm?t=1749636719\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719130/extras/4f0a13d8f4f6ed64ed3f6c0e38af3efb.mp4?t=1749636719\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2719130/extras/d266f6795b2db5b923405624fa1e266e.webp?t=1749636719\" width=600 height=50 /></span>．Original Work: Team Shanghai Alice</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Studio: YEARS STUDIO</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Producer/Performence Design: fuゆki</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Script: 帝都的天子</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Programmer: 砖块菌</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character Design: Aley琳</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Background Design/CG: Aley琳、比格沃斯先生</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CV：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kirisame Marisa: Chitose</p>",
